org.openjfx.controller

Class DBManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openjfx.controller.DBManager

  • public class DBManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Maintains the database connection throughout runtime. Connection is established at initialization. All query methods are static for use anywhere. Singleton Class.
